title: "Mid and Jungle Players ONLY. New Coaching Channel for YOU."

embed.description: Web survey powered by SurveyMonkey.com. Create your own online survey now with SurveyMonkey's expert certified FREE templates.

body:
Hey Everyone, It's Zazuu here, a Challenger Ranked 5's and Master Tier Soloq player.
I'm conducting a survey on Mid and Jungle Players , to see if I should start a Coaching/Tutorial Channel for youtube and twitch.

Here is the link to the survey: https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/WNPCLW6

It only takes a couple minutes and can end with more tutorials for YOU so you can climb the Solo q Ladder Faster than ever.


Thanks,
Zazuu.
